proof_script:
lemma shows length_sequences: "length (sequences xs) \<le> length xs" and length_asc: "ascP f \<Longrightarrow> length (asc a f ys) \<le> 1 + length ys" and length_desc: "length (desc a xs ys) \<le> 1 + length ys"
by (induct xs and a f ys and a xs ys rule: sequences_asc_desc.induct) auto
